modDescription:
This mod adds a bunch of more [coffee](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-drinks/) options to the game. Things to do with coffee, coffee crafting stations. Aristrofl like coffee. Coffee is fun.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/aristrofl/7DaysToDieMods/tree/master/CoffeeOfTheDamned)**
